1. Ona *gori* od želje da se obrazuje. (She is burning with the desire to get educated.)
2. *Gori* se već nekoliko dana. (It has been burning for several days.)
3. *Gore* se jako brzo. (It is burning quickly.)
4. U tom požaru *gori* mnogo stvari. (Many things are burning in this fire.)
5. Ona je *gorila* od sreće. (She was burning with joy.)